description: We're hitting the road! With the success of our first user conference, Elastic{ON}, we decided to tour the world and bring Elastic{ON} to you.
message: We're bringing #Elasticon back to you - starting in Chicago on October 6 and hitting 7 subsequent cities, including NYC, London, Tokyo, and more. Come join us to hear what's coming in #elasticsearch 5.0 and beyond. Get all the details here: http://go.es.io/29IVVdP
